    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Pseudolaguvia vespa, holotype, ZSI/APRC/P-1882, 30.6 mm SL; lateral, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5783231/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5783233>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ventral view showing details of thoracic adhesive apparatus in: a. Pseudolaguvia vespa, ZSI/APRC/P-1882, holotype, 30.6 mm SL; b. P. jiyaensis, CIARI/FF-76, 26.9 mm SL. Black line indicates posterior most extent of thoracic adhesive apparatus. Figure not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5783233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5783235>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ventral view showing details of papillation in: a. Pseudolaguvia vespa, ZSI/APRC/P-1882, holotype, 30.6 mm SL; b. P. jiyaensis, CIARI/FF-76, 26.9 mm SL. Yellow line indicates the region between lower lip and thoracic adhesive apparatus. Figure not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5783235/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5783237>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Pseudolaguvia vespa, ZSI/APRC/P-1882, holotype, 30.6 mm SL, showing fresh colouration." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5783237/files/figure.png" ;
